            <p>"WEBSITE" refers to (www.noxshdine.com) and (www.noxshdine.in). "RESTAURANT/RESTAURANT'S" refers all those resaturant's which are registered with us or on our website. Please Note, NOXSH DINE and NOXSHDINE refers to the same. "SERVICE/SERVICES" refers to all the  services used by CUSTOMER/BUYER AND RESTAURANT OR VISITOR or ANYONE, that are provided on NOXSHDINE website. "YOU" means any visitor, user,buyer,customer or other person who accesses our Platform or Services, whether or not such person registered for an Account, or a person or restaurant that is registered/unregistered with NOXSH DINE to use the Services. "WE", "US," OR "OUR" collectively refers to NOXSHDINE.</p>
            <p>By using our website and services, you agreed and hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms and Conditions. If you are not agree with our privacy policy and terms and conditions ,please do not use our services.</p>
            <p>We strive to provide utmost attention to our customer needs. Due to the nature of the business, NOXSHDINE hereby adheres to the following cancellation and refund policies.</p>
            <p>NOXSHDINE reserves the exclusive right to refuse or cancel any order for restaurants and services that are listed at an incorrect price or are not available or for whatsoever reasons. This is enforceable irrespective of order confirmation or payment confirmation. In such events if the payment has been processed by NOXSHDINE the amount will be refunded via the same mode of original payment and user will be notified of the same with a reasonable mode of communication. After placing an order NOXSHDINE will not entertain any user request for order cancellations.</p>
            <p>To provide the best customer satisfaction, we provide the following solutions. Feel free to contact us if you have any questions regarding the Return & Refund Policy by emailing us.</p>
        </div>

